{"tid":1578063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"612衝突受傷港台車長向警方申索","createTime":"2019-09-18T03:57:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T10:58:58.000Z","uid":147376,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7608f52dc17d93795b8dc8955acad1c2bfb8c7cc","tid":1578063,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T03:57:13.000Z","msg":"[url]612衝突受傷港台車長向警方申索<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=363102&amp;refer=Share[/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D363102%26refer%3DShare%5B%2Furl%5D&d=Ii72mHdDrz30Fn2z87Evj8orGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=ff7ea302\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D363102%26refer%3DShare%5B%2Furl%5D&h=7f429429\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=363102&amp;refer=Share[/url]</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】612衝突中，懷疑被催淚彈擊中的香港電台司機入稟區域法院，向警方就人身傷害提出申索。<br />\n<br />\n原告為香港電台外判司機莊文龍，被告是由律政司司長代表的警務處處長。入稟狀中指，6月12日莊文龍在中信大廈對出被一發催淚彈擊中頭部，而當時他已經身穿反光衣及表明他傳媒的身分，他事後一度失去意識，身體嚴重受傷，被送往瑪麗醫院急症室治理。<br />\n<br />\n他認為相關傷勢是由警方施襲，虐待或疏忽等而造成，違反普通法及人權法，要求警務處處長賠償，但未有透露索償金額。"},{"pid":"0f3a336c90b4f6aaf2b1780cde3ed23752529052","tid":1578063,"uid":55010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:08:24.000Z","msg":"識玩了"},{"pid":"bba55d080680a9e53d6ab2ecc2ff65da27f12731","tid":1578063,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:46:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fcdc8e5ded5accbfada67532d515e61833bd137","tid":1578063,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T10:55:41.000Z","msg":"仲有超過一千單"},{"pid":"ba595c17129133c0d3f3ab8613370c711b519993","tid":1578063,"uid":2054,"like":0,